                <p rend="flushleft">I. <hi rend="italic">Minutes</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council <hi rend="italic">approved</hi> the Minutes of their Third
                    Meeting.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II. <hi rend="italic">Italo-Yugoslav Frontier</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council discussed the question of the Italo-Yugoslav frontier (<gloss target="#t_CFM461">C.F.M. (46)</gloss> 5).<note n="21" xml:id="d99fn21">Dated April 27, 1946, <ref target="#pg_140">p. 140</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">III. <hi rend="italic">Date of the Next Meeting</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The next meeting of the Council of Foreign Ministers was fixed for the same day
                    (4th May) at 5 p.m./.</p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>, 8 mai, 1946.</p>
